{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.1","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Dan.003.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le grand arbre, songe de Nebucadnetsar expliqu\u00e9 par Daniel<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-27: cf. Ge 41:1-36. Job 20:5, etc. \u00c9s 2:11, 12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Nebucadnetsar, roi, \u00e0 tous les peuples, aux nations, aux hommes de toutes langues, qui habitent sur toute la terre. Que la paix vous soit donn\u00e9e avec abondance!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.2","name":"Daniel 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.3.30","name":"Daniel 3:30","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.3.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.2","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il m\u2019a sembl\u00e9 bon de faire conna\u00eetre les signes et les prodiges que le Dieu supr\u00eame a op\u00e9r\u00e9s \u00e0 mon \u00e9gard.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.3","name":"Daniel 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.1","name":"Daniel 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.3","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Que ses signes sont grands! Que ses prodiges sont puissants! Son r\u00e8gne est un r\u00e8gne \u00e9ternel, et sa domination subsiste de g\u00e9n\u00e9ration en g\u00e9n\u00e9ration.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.4","name":"Daniel 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.2","name":"Daniel 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.4","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Moi, Nebucadnetsar, je vivais tranquille dans ma maison, et heureux dans mon palais.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.5","name":"Daniel 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.3","name":"Daniel 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.5","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>J\u2019ai eu un songe qui m\u2019a effray\u00e9; les pens\u00e9es dont j\u2019\u00e9tais poursuivi sur ma couche et les visions de mon esprit me remplissaient d\u2019\u00e9pouvante.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.6","name":"Daniel 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.4","name":"Daniel 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.6","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>J\u2019ordonnai qu\u2019on f\u00eet venir devant moi tous les sages de Babylone, afin qu\u2019ils me donnassent l\u2019explication du songe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.7","name":"Daniel 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.5","name":"Daniel 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.7","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Alors vinrent les magiciens, les astrologues, les Chald\u00e9ens et les devins. Je leur dis le songe, et ils ne m\u2019en donn\u00e8rent point l\u2019explication.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.8","name":"Daniel 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.6","name":"Daniel 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.8","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>En dernier lieu, se pr\u00e9senta devant moi Daniel, nomm\u00e9 Beltschatsar d\u2019apr\u00e8s le nom de mon dieu, et qui a en lui l\u2019esprit des dieux saints. Je lui dis le songe:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.9","name":"Daniel 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.7","name":"Daniel 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.9","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Beltschatsar, chef des magiciens, qui as en toi, je le sais, l\u2019esprit des dieux saints, et pour qui aucun secret n\u2019est difficile, donne-moi l\u2019explication des visions que j\u2019ai eues en songe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.10","name":"Daniel 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.8","name":"Daniel 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.10","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Voici les visions de mon esprit, pendant que j\u2019\u00e9tais sur ma couche. Je regardais, et voici, il y avait au milieu de la terre un arbre d\u2019une grande hauteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.11","name":"Daniel 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.9","name":"Daniel 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.11","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Cet arbre \u00e9tait devenu grand et fort, sa cime s\u2019\u00e9levait jusqu\u2019aux cieux, et on le voyait des extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s de toute la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.12","name":"Daniel 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.10","name":"Daniel 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.12","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Son feuillage \u00e9tait beau, et ses fruits abondants; il portait de la nourriture pour tous; les b\u00eates des champs s\u2019abritaient sous son ombre, les oiseaux du ciel faisaient leur demeure parmi ses branches, et tout \u00eatre vivant tirait de lui sa nourriture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.13","name":"Daniel 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.11","name":"Daniel 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.13","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Dans les visions de mon esprit, que j\u2019avais sur ma couche, je regardais, et voici, un de ceux qui veillent et qui sont saints descendit des cieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.14","name":"Daniel 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.12","name":"Daniel 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.14","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il cria avec force et parla ainsi: Abattez l\u2019arbre, et coupez ses branches; secouez le feuillage, et dispersez les fruits; que les b\u00eates fuient de dessous, et les oiseaux du milieu de ses branches!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.15","name":"Daniel 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.13","name":"Daniel 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.15","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:15","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Mais laissez en terre le tronc o\u00f9 se trouvent les racines, et liez-le avec des cha\u00eenes de fer et d\u2019airain, parmi l\u2019herbe des champs. Qu\u2019il soit tremp\u00e9 de la ros\u00e9e du ciel, et qu\u2019il ait, comme les b\u00eates, l\u2019herbe de la terre pour partage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.16","name":"Daniel 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.14","name":"Daniel 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.16","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:16","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Son c\u0153ur d\u2019homme lui sera \u00f4t\u00e9, et un c\u0153ur de b\u00eate lui sera donn\u00e9; et sept temps passeront sur lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.17","name":"Daniel 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.15","name":"Daniel 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.17","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:17","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Cette sentence est un d\u00e9cret de ceux qui veillent, cette r\u00e9solution est un ordre des saints, afin que les vivants sachent que le Tr\u00e8s-Haut domine sur le r\u00e8gne des hommes, qu\u2019il le donne \u00e0 qui il lui pla\u00eet, et qu\u2019il y \u00e9l\u00e8ve le plus vil des hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.18","name":"Daniel 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.16","name":"Daniel 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.18","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:18","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Voil\u00e0 le songe que j\u2019ai eu, moi, le roi Nebucadnetsar. Toi, Beltschatsar, donnes-en l\u2019explication, puisque tous les sages de mon royaume ne peuvent me la donner; toi, tu le peux, car tu as en toi l\u2019esprit des dieux saints.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.19","name":"Daniel 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.17","name":"Daniel 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.19","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:19","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Alors Daniel, nomm\u00e9 Beltschatsar, fut un moment stup\u00e9fait, et ses pens\u00e9es le troublaient. Le roi reprit et dit: Beltschatsar, que le songe et l\u2019explication ne te troublent pas! Et Beltschatsar r\u00e9pondit: Mon seigneur, que le songe soit pour tes ennemis, et son explication pour tes adversaires!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.20","name":"Daniel 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.18","name":"Daniel 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.20","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:20","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>L\u2019arbre que tu as vu, qui \u00e9tait devenu grand et fort, dont la cime s\u2019\u00e9levait jusqu\u2019aux cieux, et qu\u2019on voyait de tous les points de la terre;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.21","name":"Daniel 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.19","name":"Daniel 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.21","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:21","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>cet arbre, dont le feuillage \u00e9tait beau et les fruits abondants, qui portait de la nourriture pour tous, sous lequel s\u2019abritaient les b\u00eates des champs, et parmi les branches duquel les oiseaux du ciel faisaient leur demeure,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.22","name":"Daniel 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.20","name":"Daniel 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.22","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:22","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>c\u2019est toi, \u00f4 roi, qui es devenu grand et fort, dont la grandeur s\u2019est accrue et s\u2019est \u00e9lev\u00e9e jusqu\u2019aux cieux, et dont la domination s\u2019\u00e9tend jusqu\u2019aux extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s de la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.23","name":"Daniel 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.21","name":"Daniel 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.23","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:23","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Le roi a vu l\u2019un de ceux qui veillent et qui sont saints descendre des cieux et dire: Abattez l\u2019arbre, et d\u00e9truisez-le; mais laissez en terre le tronc o\u00f9 se trouvent les racines, et liez-le avec des cha\u00eenes de fer et d\u2019airain, parmi l\u2019herbe des champs; qu\u2019il soit tremp\u00e9 de la ros\u00e9e du ciel, et que son partage soit avec les b\u00eates des champs, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que sept temps soient pass\u00e9s sur lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.24","name":"Daniel 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.22","name":"Daniel 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.24","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:24","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Voici l\u2019explication, \u00f4 roi, voici le d\u00e9cret du Tr\u00e8s-Haut, qui s\u2019accomplira sur mon seigneur le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.25","name":"Daniel 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.23","name":"Daniel 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.25","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:25","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>On te chassera du milieu des hommes, tu auras ta demeure avec les b\u00eates des champs, et l\u2019on te donnera comme aux b\u0153ufs de l\u2019herbe \u00e0 manger; tu seras tremp\u00e9 de la ros\u00e9e du ciel, et sept temps passeront sur toi, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que tu saches que le Tr\u00e8s-Haut domine sur le r\u00e8gne des hommes et qu\u2019il le donne \u00e0 qui il lui pla\u00eet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.26","name":"Daniel 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.24","name":"Daniel 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.26","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:26","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>L\u2019ordre de laisser le tronc o\u00f9 se trouvent les racines de l\u2019arbre signifie que ton royaume te restera quand tu reconna\u00eetras que celui qui domine est dans les cieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.27","name":"Daniel 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.25","name":"Daniel 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.27","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:27","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, \u00f4 roi, puisse mon conseil te plaire! Mets un terme \u00e0 tes p\u00e9ch\u00e9s en pratiquant la justice, et \u00e0 tes iniquit\u00e9s en usant de compassion envers les malheureux, et ton bonheur pourra se prolonger.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.28","name":"Daniel 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.26","name":"Daniel 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.28","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:28","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.029,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 28-37: cf. Da 5:18-21. (Pr 16:18. Ja 4:6, 10. Ps 75:5-8.) Ro 1:21, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Toutes ces choses se sont accomplies sur le roi Nebucadnetsar.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.29","name":"Daniel 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.27","name":"Daniel 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.29","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:29","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Au bout de douze mois, comme il se promenait dans le palais royal \u00e0 Babylone,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.30","name":"Daniel 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.28","name":"Daniel 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.30","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:30","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>le roi prit la parole et dit: N\u2019est-ce pas ici Babylone la grande, que j\u2019ai b\u00e2tie, comme r\u00e9sidence royale, par la puissance de ma force et pour la gloire de ma magnificence?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.31","name":"Daniel 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.29","name":"Daniel 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.31","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:31","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>La parole \u00e9tait encore dans la bouche du roi, qu\u2019une voix descendit du ciel: Apprends, roi Nebucadnetsar, qu\u2019on va t\u2019enlever le royaume.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.32","name":"Daniel 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.30","name":"Daniel 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.32","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:32","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>On te chassera du milieu des hommes, tu auras ta demeure avec les b\u00eates des champs, on te donnera comme aux b\u0153ufs de l\u2019herbe \u00e0 manger; et sept temps passeront sur toi, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que tu saches que le Tr\u00e8s-Haut domine sur le r\u00e8gne des hommes et qu\u2019il le donne \u00e0 qui il lui pla\u00eet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.33","name":"Daniel 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.31","name":"Daniel 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.33","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:33","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Au m\u00eame instant la parole s\u2019accomplit sur Nebucadnetsar. Il fut chass\u00e9 du milieu des hommes, il mangea de l\u2019herbe comme les b\u0153ufs, son corps fut tremp\u00e9 de la ros\u00e9e du ciel; jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que ses cheveux crussent comme les plumes des aigles, et ses ongles comme ceux des oiseaux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.34","name":"Daniel 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.32","name":"Daniel 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.34","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:34","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s le temps marqu\u00e9, moi, Nebucadnetsar, je levai les yeux vers le ciel, et la raison me revint. J\u2019ai b\u00e9ni le Tr\u00e8s-Haut, j\u2019ai lou\u00e9 et glorifi\u00e9 celui qui vit \u00e9ternellement, celui dont la domination est une domination \u00e9ternelle, et dont le r\u00e8gne subsiste de g\u00e9n\u00e9ration en g\u00e9n\u00e9ration.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.35","name":"Daniel 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.33","name":"Daniel 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.35","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:35","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Tous les habitants de la terre ne sont \u00e0 ses yeux que n\u00e9ant: il agit comme il lui pla\u00eet avec l\u2019arm\u00e9e des cieux et avec les habitants de la terre, et il n\u2019y a personne qui r\u00e9siste \u00e0 sa main et qui lui dise: Que fais-tu?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.36","name":"Daniel 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.34","name":"Daniel 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.36","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:36","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.004.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>En ce temps, la raison me revint; la gloire de mon royaume, ma magnificence et ma splendeur me furent rendues; mes conseillers et mes grands me redemand\u00e8rent; je fus r\u00e9tabli dans mon royaume, et ma puissance ne fit que s\u2019accro\u00eetre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.37","name":"Daniel 4:37","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.35","name":"Daniel 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.37","label":"","reference":"Daniel 4:37","prev_osis_id":"Dan.004.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.4.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Maintenant, moi, Nebucadnetsar, je loue, j\u2019exalte et je glorifie le roi des cieux, dont toutes les \u0153uvres sont vraies et les voies justes, et qui peut abaisser ceux qui marchent avec orgueil.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.4","name":"Daniel 4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.5.1","name":"Daniel 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.4.36","name":"Daniel 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.4.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb7cf22b4.48165184');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb7cf22b4.48165184\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb7cf22b4.48165184","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb7cf22b4.48165184'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb7cf22b4.48165184\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}